data.description: Deal FELL!!  Buyer lost financing!  2022 Mayor's Historical Preservation Excellence Award Recipient in Tanner Historic. 2 Flat in Great Condition! PROPERTY IS SOLD AS-IS. Gorgeous Blackhawk Park across the street! New gutters & downspouts; stucco rehabbed w/ historically approved materials and 25 yr warranty Rhinoshield ceramic paint. New cedar stairs and rail. Water heaters, bathrooms remodeled & c/a installed in 2017. New Screen Doors in 2020.  Hardwood Floors and Natural Woodwork throughout! Each Apartment (Upper & Lower units) consists of Living Room, Dining Room, Kitchen, Two Bedrooms, and one Bath. Both apartments have access to the basement with storage and 2 Laundry hookups.. Off-Street Parking! All Appliances included! All Utilities are separate. Owner occupied since 2015. Property is zoned R-4 and is licensed with the city of Aurora.  Live in one, let your tenant pay the mortgage!!  DO NOT WAIT...OFFERS WILL BE ACCEPTED UNTIL MONDAY 12/18/2023 BY 5:00 PM. Best offer will be accepted and property SOLD!
